Trustee_3.name: Maria Rossi
Trustee_3.content: Maria Rossi has demonstrated strong competence and trustworthiness throughout the investment process. She successfully adhered to the proposed allocation plan and managed investor resources responsibly, leading to a solid profit outcome for both parties. Her commitment to fair profit distribution and transparency has enhanced her credibility as a trustee. She is recognized for her pro-social behavior by prioritizing efficient management and clear communication with her investor, Fatima Ali.

Investor_17.name: Fatima Ali
Investor_17.content: Fatima Ali has demonstrated reliability and a willingness to engage in a fair profit-sharing agreement. Her prompt contribution and acceptance of the profit distribution reflect positively on her pro-sociality and trustworthiness. She has established a strong initial interaction with her trustee, indicating potential for fruitful collaboration in future investments.
